@1864 = ~Thank you, <CHARNAME>. (She leans into you again and hugs you close) I love you. You're so much more than I deserve.~
@1865 = ~(She chuckles and shakes her head) That's okay... and thank you. (She leans into you again and hugs you close) I love you. You're so much more than I deserve.~
@1866 = ~And so what? That I don't have the right to be sure that I want to sleep with you? Once a whore, always a whore?~
@1867 = ~No! No, that's not what I meant! I'm sorry. I know you've had a difficult time with men in the past, and I should be a little more sensitive, but let's just say that the "big" head isn't doing all the thinking at the moment.~
