@1870 = ~Well, it does. I want to be sure, <CHARNAME>. I love you... (sigh)... but I don't always understand you. No matter. I'll work it out.~
@1871 = ~I know I do. I suppose it's in my nature. To be honest, I don't mean anything by it. (grin) If it *did* mean anything, you would know! So what are you saying? That you want me to stop teasing you?~
@1872 = ~No, of course not. It's funny, although I'll admit I don't like it when you do it to other people! I want to keep you all to myself. (wrap her in a hug)~
@1873 = ~No, you know I don't. I love the way you tease me. But I'm sorry. I know you've had a difficult time with men in the past, and I should be a little more sensitive, but let's just say that the "big" head isn't doing all the thinking at the moment.~
