@1875 = ~(She hugs you back) That's alright. I want you to keep me all to yourself too. I love you... you're more than I deserve.~
@1876 = ~<CHARNAME>, I love you, you know that... (sigh)... but I don't always understand you. No matter. I'll work it out.~

