@1896 = ~You're... not interested? I want you, here, <CHARNAME>... now. After what we spoke of last time... do... do you not love me anymore?~
@1897 = ~It's actually what you said that got me thinking, Fade. I do love you, I'm just not ready to love you like that yet. Too much is going on. I'm sorry.~
