@1904 = ~(She pulls you close to her and kisses you softly, softer than you would imagine Fade capable of. She then guides you to the ground, and then stands over you. Slowly, almost teasingly, she removes her clothes, until she is clad in nothing more than her tattoos. She is lightly muscled, and again you notice that she is rather more curvaceous than other elves you have met)~
@1905 = ~Unusual? You thought me unusual, nothing more? So once again I am destined to be an oddity, an exotic, there for the pleasure of all? I'm glad you told me this, <CHARNAME>, for now I see you are no different from everyone else who has tried to use me! And I will NOT be used again!~
